The Great British Sewing Bee - Series 3, Episode 2




The nine remaining amateur sewers prepare to do battle again, in a bid to bag garment of the week and secure their place in the running to win The Great British Sewing Bee. The three challenges this week test the sewers' ability to make clothes on a miniature scale.




Original Air Date: 12-Feb-2015
